CentralDataRepository Uses Docs:

Actions Supportted:

 Reload/Restore
 Refress
 Search    :
 FirstLoad : initial load for trending

    steps:
            1. Instanciate CentralDataRepository and obtain its instance
            2. provide appropriate Flag and actionCompleteCallback
            3. Register Adapters for data Update Listeners

Note: (For Search)
                onSearch() save 'search term' to SharedPreferences and follow above steps,
                every things will be settled down.
